  "title": "WAREHOUSE CUSTOMER SERVICE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>Provide admin support to the Warehouse Team, the incumbent will be involved in general\nadmin duties as such:</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />\n- Administrative duties involving warehouse coordination activities - PO, DO,\nInvoices.</p><p>- Co-ordination with Customers and freight forwarders for PO delivery &\ncontainer truck-in schedule.</p><p>- Ensures proper documentation not limiting to sorting, filing and archiving.</p><p>- Perform data entry work to ensure the accuracy and confidentiality of\ninformation is capture in the system.</p><p>- Handle inquiries from customers, colleagues and management etc.</p><p>- Responsible for effective administrative/clerical function in the warehouse\noffice.</p><p>- Other ad hoc duties as per assigned</p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><p>- 1-2 years of related administrative experience.</p><p>- Experience in high volume inventory coordination work</p><p>- Able to multi-task with excellent coordination skills</p><p>- Good with MS office such as words, excel </p><p>- Knowledge in WMS will be advantaged</p><p>- Meticulous and independent, good communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>- Able to work in a fast-paced environment and must be comfortable working in warehouse\nenvironment</p>",
